# Title: Mesh Agent Service Installation
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-11-28
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects a Mesh Agent service installation. Mesh Agent is used to remotely manage computers
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.t1219.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/system/service_control_manager/win_system_service_install_mesh_agent.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate use of the tool

EventID=7045 Provider_Name="Service Control Manager" ImagePath="*MeshAgent.exe*" OR ServiceName="*Mesh Agent*"